offset_bottom = 567.0
theme_override_colors/font_color = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
text = "Welcome to the system. Your goal is simple: extract wealth through digital deception.
Run surveillance on potential targets by navigating the database.
Infiltrate the Contacts app to find and select your next victim.
Target vulnerabilities to execute successful hacks or social engineering scams.
Every piece of data you find increases your chances of a massive payout.
Dive deep into their personal history to make your scams more believable.
Inspect the Calls app to open and review their recent call logs.
Analyze who they talk to; knowing their inner circle is the key to a perfect sting.
Remember: information is the most valuable currency on this desktop.
You are the ghost in the machine—stay sharp and stay undetected.
					


Operations can be expanded beyond just the basic communication tools.
Never hesitate to explore; every icon on this screen serves a purpose.
Be curious and test the other applications available on the system.
Research every corner of the OS, as hidden data can lead to bigger scores.
Observe how different apps interact to find new ways to exploit the victims.
Watch for clues in files, notes, or system settings that others might overlook.
Seize every opportunity to drain accounts before the security protocols kick in.
Exploit the system to its full potential and dominate the digital underworld.
Reap the rewards of your technical prowess and leave no trace behind."
vertical_alignment = 1

